title: No. 18 Michigan dominates No. 13 Northwestern 38-0
text:
> Top News No. 18 Michigan dominates No. 13 Northwestern 38-0 Michigan wide receiver Jehu Chesson (86) evades a tackle from Northwestern safety Godwin Igwebuike (16) as he returns the opening kickoff 96 yards for a touchdown during the first quarter of an NCAA college football game in Ann Arbor, Mich., Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Tony Ding)
